00:20:14.060 --> 00:20:18.980
you take waste heat,
relatively low temperature,

00:20:18.980 --> 00:20:23.210
from electric generation,
and you pipe it around

00:20:23.210 --> 00:20:25.280
to heat buildings.

00:20:25.280 --> 00:20:27.710
The Danes did a lot of this.

00:20:27.710 --> 00:20:29.630
One of the readings
mentions that.

00:20:29.630 --> 00:20:34.820
It's also interesting, the
Soviets did a lot of it.

00:20:34.820 --> 00:20:38.720
It requires you to have
power plants relatively close

00:20:38.720 --> 00:20:40.640
to offices or
factories or homes,

00:20:40.640 --> 00:20:42.380
so it's not the greatest thing.

00:20:42.380 --> 00:20:46.010
